List all available Leadbay lenses (saved lead-search configurations). Each lens defines a different target market or buyer segment. The lens with `is_last_active=true` is used by default for lead discovery.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} when the user wants to switch lens or asks "what lenses do I have".

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} in normal flow — composites auto-resolve the active lens via `/me.last_requested_lens`.
